{"tid":106050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[轟啊] 重慶玩機動遊戲被拋出 少女墮地慘死","createTime":"2017-02-03T10:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T07:10:59.000Z","uid":41205,"like":47,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08ae3271753b6a93525b66b018a4105c4009f3f9","tid":106050,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:48:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170203&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56258169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170203%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56258169&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=8d58dbe9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170203%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56258169&h=583b788d\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170203&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56258169</a><br />\n<br />\n重慶豐都今日發生恐怖機動遊戲意外，一名遊客在一個名叫「遨游太空」的機動遊戲時，疑安全帶突然斷裂，致被拋至半空，落地時撞向旁邊圍欄，送院後傷重不治。據網民指，該名遊客為一名16歲少女。<br />\n<br />\n事發今日下午2時，豐都朝華公園「遨游太空」是公園其中一個熱門的機動遊戲，每人每次收費15元人民幣。現場民眾拍到的片段顯示，機動遊戲高速轉動的時候，女子被拋出座位，初時還能抓住扶手，及後則被拋到半空，現場目擊事故的民眾不斷驚叫。片段又顯示女子落地後，初時仍有知覺，公園的工作人員為她急救，並召喚救護車到場，將地送到當地醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n當地宣傳部人員稱，這名女子送院搶救後，傷重不治，目前事故原因仍在調查。"},{"pid":"e184444011e9ab9e3b83b63dd9a4c9762f4fbf59","tid":106050,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a98c44bb2291c77085122e81ee58df913c8944","tid":106050,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:51:26.000Z","msg":"竟然得一個"},{"pid":"e80eccd247e6a204562f5dd0752bad842aa3dc63","tid":106050,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:53:26.000Z